        <message>**If your laptop has been stolen or lost:**
1. Report the incident to your line manager
2. Obtain a valid affidavit detailing the loss or theft from the SAPS
3. Ask your manager or a colleague to log an insurance claim request on your behalf on the IT Service Portal
4. Email the SAPS validated affidavit to the insurance claims coordinator 

Once the Claims team has  assessed and validated the claim and affidavit, you will be provided with a replacement device.</message>
